{
  "id": "RAW_666b15",
  "title": "谷歌终于登顶一次了！最强推理模型 Gemini 2.5 Pro 实测体验，真的有点东西",
  "url": "https://www.jiqizhixin.com/articles/2025-03-26-7",
  "date": "2025-03-26 08:52:18",
  "author": "机器之心",
  "siteName": "机器之心",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <section data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" data-style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-bottom: 0px; outline: 0px; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-wrap: wrap; caret-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; visibility: visible; line-height: 27.2px; color: rgb(163, 163, 163) !important;\">\n   <section data-style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; outline: 0px; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px; visibility: visible; line-height: 27.2px;\">\n    <section data-style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; outline: 0px; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px; visibility: visible; line-height: 27.2px;\">\n     <section data-color=\"rgb(117, 117, 118)\" data-custom=\"rgb(117, 117, 118)\" data-id=\"85660\" data-style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; outline: 0px; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: currentcolor; visibility: visible; line-height: 27.2px;\">\n      <section data-style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 2em; padding-top: 0.5em; padding-bottom: 0.5em; outline: 0px; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-right-style: none; border-left-style: none; text-decoration: inherit; visibility: visible; line-height: 27.2px;\">\n       <blockquote data-author-name=\"\" data-content-utf8-length=\"15\" data-source-title=\"\" data-type=\"2\" data-url=\"\">\n        <section>\n         <section>\n          谷歌有史以来最智能的 AI 模型。\n         </section>\n        </section>\n       </blockquote>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   深夜悄悄搞事情的不只 OpenAI，抢在 OpenAI 开直播之前，谷歌上线了最强大的推理模型 Gemini 2.5 Pro。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   谷歌 CEO「劈柴哥」甚至用：「这是谷歌有史以来最智能的 AI 模型。」为它站台。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img alt=\"图片\" data-imgfileid=\"503478328\" data-ratio=\"0.6042105263157894\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/82b45f50-c582-41e6-a2df-537b68dc4900/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"950\" data-original-style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;\" data-index=\"1\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/b2e54067-1cc8-4ed3-a5f8-9d48ae927ab7/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"0\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   不过，从 Gemini 2.5 Pro 的成绩单来看，它可能确实担得起「有史以来最强」的名号。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   首先来看推理能力，在被视为人类给 AI 的终极考验的 Humanity's Last Exam 基准测试中，不额外调用工具的 Gemini 2.5 Pro 取得了 18.8% 的准确率，超过了能秒解图论难题的 OpenAI o3-mini（high）。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   和推理能力强相关的科学和数学能力，在 GPQA、AIME 2025 等主流基础测试中，Gemini 2.5 Pro 也是遥遥领先，具体成绩如下：\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img alt=\"image.png\" data-imgfileid=\"503478329\" data-ratio=\"0.614\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/7107b3f4-29c4-4ae7-6a69-57beaa83a500/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1000\" data-original-style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;\" data-index=\"2\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/aacff696-515b-4efc-a9e9-ce03b448677f/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"1\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img alt=\"图片\" data-imgfileid=\"503478331\" data-ratio=\"1.1376673040152965\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5dbf2403-8a85-4655-149b-c2cbb7179100/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1046\" data-original-style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;\" data-index=\"3\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/6cfd0ab8-357f-4ab9-9625-65d8140a40d7/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"2\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   在编程能力方面，Gemini 2.5 Pro 相比 2.0 实现了质的飞跃，未来还将不断增强。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   其中，SWE-bench 衡量的是编码能力，Aider Polyglot 衡量的是模型的代码编辑水平。除了在 Agentic coding 方面逊色于 Claude 3.7 Sonnet，Gemini 2.5 Pro 均斩获第一：\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img alt=\"图片\" data-imgfileid=\"503478333\" data-ratio=\"0.5370370370370371\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/10cc769c-ee03-4a43-8983-2461417ec000/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-original-style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;\" data-index=\"4\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/02592a90-4173-4fa7-9b5f-20100d69d5ac/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"3\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   谷歌称 Gemini 2.5 Pro 比较擅长在创建视觉效果精美的网页应用和操作智能体。在官方放出的 demo 中，只需一行提示词，Gemini 2.5 Pro 就开动脑筋，逐步推理出了这个类似「flappy bird」的小游戏的全部代码，并且直接可玩：<a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/unlZoM5oCH3HCw2kxy6X_w\"><img src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/0d7a2b40-4687-402c-9812-314c20de8d56/1742978822066.png\" style=\"width: 70%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></a>\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   再来是对话能力，在大模型竞技场 Chatbot Arena 的榜单上，Gemini 2.5 Pro 以绝对优势强势登顶，创下了前所未有的最大分数飞跃，比 Grok - 3 和 GPT - 4.5 高接近 40 分：\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img alt=\"图片\" data-imgfileid=\"503478334\" data-ratio=\"0.85\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3714bee7-5c31-4db7-3d38-6922c8275200/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"900\" data-original-style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;\" data-index=\"5\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/c7d65ca8-423a-4bd2-b1a5-a2cea1d6df41/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"4\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   从第二名以下的成绩，不难发现，Chatbot Arena 的前几名分差往往很小，几乎不超过 10 分。Grok-3 上个月刚登顶，第一的位置还没坐几个月，就被 Gemini 2.5 Pro 甩开了。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   除了对话能力，Gemini 2.5 Pro 在 Chatbot Arena 的复杂指令、编程、数学、创意写作、指令跟随的榜单上也是全面领先，堪称「六边形战士」。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img alt=\"图片\" data-imgfileid=\"503478335\" data-ratio=\"0.8537037037037037\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/27c908b5-17e4-481a-6ad1-d49929af6500/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-original-style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;\" data-index=\"6\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/33d6455a-ae20-404f-83e8-00ca37260449/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"5\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   和其他家推理模型不同的是，Gemini 2.5 延续了 Gemini 系列模型的核心优势 —— 原生多模态能力和长上下文窗口。Gemini 2.5 Pro 版本拥有 100 万 token 的上下文窗口（没有缩减，即将提升至 200 万 token），支持文本、音频、图像、视频及完整代码库输入。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img alt=\"图片\" data-imgfileid=\"503478336\" data-ratio=\"1.1537037037037037\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1411d83d-7c1a-4de4-cd56-cd1eeeb04000/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-original-style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;\" data-index=\"7\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/f3dca893-c48b-4700-bc25-06b980610ff8/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"6\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 50%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <em><sup>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 支持把图像转化为可以 3D 打印的格式。</sup></em>\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   从 Vision Arena 榜单来看，Gemini 2.5 Pro 不止支持原生多模态，能力更是一骑绝尘。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img alt=\"图片\" data-imgfileid=\"503478338\" data-ratio=\"0.8537037037037037\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/28403977-6059-4c8a-b7fb-83135ee8ef00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-original-style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;\" data-index=\"8\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/a1b58362-7e9c-4329-8c88-5af77ca20ba2/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"7\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   防盗水印一秒蒸发、证件照 10 秒抠图，以下是第四名 Gemini-2.0-flash-thinking 「一句话 P 图」的效果。如今，在新的第一名面前，更是被远远超越。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img alt=\"图片\" data-imgfileid=\"503478339\" data-ratio=\"0.6648148148148149\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4f1efd01-2fda-4100-234a-d4283f617600/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-original-style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;\" data-index=\"9\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/48a55608-3d29-413c-b990-1fa49a296021/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"8\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   作为一个会「思考」的模型，Gemini 2.5 Pro 专为复杂任务设计，更够能智能地分析信息、理解问题的背景和情境以及做出明智的决策。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   不过，谷歌并未公开技术报告，我们只能从谷歌放出的博客中得知，他们的技术突破在于强化学习、思维链提示和后训练。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img alt=\"图片\" data-imgfileid=\"503478340\" data-ratio=\"0.4287037037037037\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/7497333f-66e3-4bef-688e-1f6a34ab8000/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-original-style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;\" data-index=\"10\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/3be1b822-b0f3-40ce-9b7b-a5cf222bf848/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"9\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   现在登录 Google AI Studio，普通用户和企业就能体验到 Gemini 2.5 Pro。如果是高贵的 Gemini Advanced 用户，在桌面和移动设备下来菜单，就能直接使用了。未来几周内，Gemini 2.5 Pro 也将登陆 Vertex AI 平台。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img alt=\"图片\" data-imgfileid=\"503478341\" data-ratio=\"0.6374207188160677\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/59cbe7bc-e31a-4a09-1d89-64a34dddbd00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"946\" data-original-style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;\" data-index=\"11\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/93916f5c-757c-4caf-b92a-178254f01efe/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"10\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   其实前几天，Chatbot Arena 上就有一个代号「Nebula」的神秘模型在 LMSYS Arena 屠榜，击败了包括 o1、o3-mini 和 Claude 3.7 Thinking 在内的众多对手。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   不知道是不是谷歌偷师了 OpenAI 的营销技巧，正式公布 Gemini 2.5 Pro 之前，劈柴哥也神秘兮兮地发了一条推特：\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img alt=\"图片\" data-imgfileid=\"503478342\" data-ratio=\"1.198744769874477\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/927195af-e501-44ff-16b4-78dd2f9da600/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"956\" data-original-style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;\" data-index=\"12\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/d58860ad-2417-4bcd-a8ea-9389dc8e4099/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"11\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 50%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   不过现在再模仿「strawberry」可能有点晚了，遇到大佬无缘无故开始在社交平台上发「诗和远方」，都可以召唤 Grok 来甄别。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img alt=\"图片\" data-imgfileid=\"503478343\" data-ratio=\"0.3395061728395062\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c775ceb7-a012-447e-9b97-5616c3a26a00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"972\" data-original-style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;\" data-index=\"13\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/e02ffa2e-6d4f-4e14-94d5-de01941b078d/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"12\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <strong>一手实测</strong>\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   看完了成绩单，Gemini 2.5 Pro 的实际水平是否也如此出色呢？\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   实测见真章，机器之心先对它的推理、数学、科学和编程四个方面展开了一番测评。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <strong>推理</strong>\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   根据之前测试推理模型的经验，我们总结了几道很难答对的逻辑题来考验 Gemini 2.5 Pro。\n  </section>\n  <blockquote data-author-name=\"\" data-content-utf8-length=\"50\" data-source-title=\"\" data-type=\"2\" data-url=\"\">\n   <section>\n    <section>\n     提示词：两个人同时来到了河边，都想过河，但只有一条小船，而且小船只能载一个人。请问：他们能否都过河？\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </blockquote>\n  <section>\n   <img data-galleryid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"503478348\" data-ratio=\"0.5398886827458256\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3edbdc38-b0ed-424f-40da-2b78dec65900/public\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1078\" data-original-style=\"\" data-index=\"14\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/dd39cb6d-acba-4098-b244-fad9b573029e/640.gif\" data-order=\"0\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"13\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   仅用了 11 秒，Gemini 2.5 Pro 成功识破了逻辑陷阱：「两个人同时来到了河边」不一定都在同岸，如果是对岸就成立了。\n  </section>\n  <blockquote data-author-name=\"\" data-content-utf8-length=\"102\" data-source-title=\"\" data-type=\"2\" data-url=\"\">\n   <section>\n    <section>\n     <section>\n      提示词：校长室的玻璃被人用足球砸坏了，有四个人被校长怀疑，四人依次陈述自己理由，其中有一个人说法很可疑，他就是肇事者。\n     </section>\n     <section>\n      甲：我没有砸玻璃。\n     </section>\n     <section>\n      乙：甲说的是对的。\n     </section>\n     <section>\n      丙：丁在说谎。\n     </section>\n     <section>\n      丁：我没有玩足球。\n     </section>\n     <section>\n      请问肇事者是谁？\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </blockquote>\n  <section>\n   <img data-imgfileid=\"503478350\" data-ratio=\"0.531047265987025\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/af0a37ba-8273-4abd-bdf8-93f4a561f900/public\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1079\" data-original-style=\"\" data-index=\"15\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/d6668601-42ec-4595-9b53-78bde22b6c04/640.gif\" data-order=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"15\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   这回 Gemini 2.5 Pro 的思考时间长了一点，但是由于它忽略了在现实中丙的发言顺序在丁之前，所以丙说的一定为假，因此正确答案是丙，Gemini 2.5 Pro 答错了。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   其他推理模型很难搞定的图推题，Gemini 2.5 Pro 也能一次答对。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img data-imgfileid=\"503478352\" data-ratio=\"0.531047265987025\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4af886de-c7ae-48a9-56e6-50c8826a6a00/public\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1079\" data-original-style=\"\" data-index=\"16\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/3c449bdc-99f1-475f-8a8e-898e83278afd/640.gif\" data-order=\"2\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"14\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <strong>数学</strong>\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   要检验推理模型的有多聪明，数学题是最好的「智商测试」，我们先来一道今年的考研数学真题：\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img data-imgfileid=\"503478353\" data-ratio=\"0.531047265987025\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1a227691-bbee-4b69-d6a4-e240d4d8d600/public\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1079\" data-original-style=\"\" data-index=\"17\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/df7c9e62-f6c6-4266-84f1-345f891e5b87/640.gif\" data-order=\"3\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"19\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   过程和结果，Gemini 2.5 Pro 都轻松拿下。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   再上点强度，来一道 IMO 2024 年的真题：\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img data-imgfileid=\"503478354\" data-ratio=\"0.531047265987025\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/fd292864-6849-41e7-20f9-fa206c731a00/public\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1079\" data-original-style=\"\" data-index=\"18\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/d210a79e-9783-4bb5-ba6b-95c725d7a4d3/640.gif\" data-order=\"4\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"17\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   一阵强劲的思考过后，Gemini 2.5 Pro 给出的答案也是正确的。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img alt=\"图片\" data-imgfileid=\"503478355\" data-ratio=\"0.3861111111111111\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/dd1573a9-29e4-48ba-6132-aaf9e7851000/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-original-style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;\" data-index=\"19\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/d3e4f208-880f-4379-8794-46fdd3499515/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"16\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   拼多多砍一刀背后蕴含的「极限」思想，也没难倒它。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img data-imgfileid=\"503478356\" data-ratio=\"0.531047265987025\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2f284c9c-f5a6-415f-3f2b-8ae3273c9000/public\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1079\" data-original-style=\"\" data-index=\"20\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/1a564225-ab7f-4cc7-b081-2739df739530/640.gif\" data-order=\"5\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"18\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <strong>科学</strong>\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   来一道 2023 年理综物理真题 ——\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img alt=\"image.png\" data-imgfileid=\"503478357\" data-ratio=\"0.18333333333333332\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1ae0bd5c-cd01-4d54-ac2e-1257f276a900/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-original-style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;\" data-index=\"21\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/4474cb26-3338-4bd0-ae4b-b726641bee04/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"20\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   Gemini 2.5 Pro 稍加思考，轻松回答出正确答案。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img data-galleryid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"503478322\" data-ratio=\"0.4981226533166458\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/35cd05ea-b869-4926-2bc7-2505d91f5700/public\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"799\" data-original-style=\"\" data-index=\"22\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/b94315de-45cb-4233-b548-9a55232ca378/640.gif\" data-order=\"6\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"21\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img alt=\"image.png\" data-imgfileid=\"503478362\" data-ratio=\"0.4824074074074074\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d93a4a19-8549-4568-eda4-e1aae808d900/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-original-style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;\" data-index=\"23\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/23a08fc1-2736-4def-8edc-759da82899e2/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"22\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   Gemini 2.0 Flash 则遗憾离场。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img alt=\"image.png\" data-imgfileid=\"503478361\" data-ratio=\"0.47685185185185186\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/de3b4025-89da-4d1c-ff91-a1a404945500/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-original-style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;\" data-index=\"24\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/939ffcaf-8571-4b71-9d9f-46b9b8c1bfa8/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"23\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <strong>编程</strong>\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   我们先让 Gemini 2.5 Pro 生成一个贪吃蛇游戏。\n  </section>\n  <blockquote data-author-name=\"\" data-content-utf8-length=\"261\" data-source-title=\"\" data-type=\"2\" data-url=\"\">\n   <section>\n    <section>\n     「创建一个经典的贪吃蛇小游戏，游戏界面为 400 × 400 像素的画布。蛇由若干个 10 × 10 像素的方块组成，初始长度为 3 个方块，初始位置在画布中心。蛇可以向上、向下、向左、向右移动，使用键盘的方向键控制蛇的移动方向。游戏中随机生成一个 10 × 10 像素的红色食物，当蛇吃到食物时，长度增加 1 个方块，分数增加 10 分，并重新生成食物。如果蛇撞到画布边界或自身，则游戏结束，弹出一个对话框显示最终得分，并提供重新开始的选项。游戏开始时，蛇以中等速度移动，随着时间的推移逐渐加快速度，增加游戏的挑战性。」\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </blockquote>\n  <section>\n   Gemini 2.5 Pro 表示毫无压力，还贴心附上操作指南。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img data-galleryid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"503478323\" data-ratio=\"0.4956195244055069\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/68b82c2c-98ee-4c4a-071f-d1c93c036f00/public\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"799\" data-original-style=\"\" data-index=\"25\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/acdf528f-a0ec-4a99-a0bd-c1c93702e293/640.gif\" data-order=\"7\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"25\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img alt=\"image.png\" data-imgfileid=\"503478360\" data-ratio=\"0.4566744730679157\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/759167cc-4153-46c1-abad-666e3bb27400/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"854\" data-original-style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;\" data-index=\"26\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/ddfa3c48-a780-416a-8de5-d7681449ae1a/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"24\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img data-galleryid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"503478325\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/52c8f685-46c9-436f-01b3-f8aeff47f900/public\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"330\" data-original-style=\"\" data-index=\"27\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/032ca490-6d23-40eb-b60e-1918b95ce3c9/640.gif\" data-order=\"8\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"26\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 50%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   然后上点难度「增加不可移动的障碍物（地图边缘 + 随机 3 个方块）」。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img data-galleryid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"503478326\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a2a84c7e-13be-4f19-2296-0fda8c654b00/public\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"330\" data-original-style=\"\" data-index=\"28\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/2030132c-0011-453a-b815-15cb0824645a/640.gif\" data-order=\"9\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"27\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 50%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   再来添加一点 buff「添加特殊道具（吃到的效果任选 2 种）：加速 / 减速道具，临时穿墙（10 秒），清除所有障碍物」。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img data-galleryid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"503478327\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/22b39c11-d796-46f7-2c8a-8e02b5cd9900/public\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"330\" data-original-style=\"\" data-index=\"29\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/37510e48-f78e-4d8d-a752-520b63abb9d7/640.gif\" data-order=\"10\" alt=\"图片\" data-report-img-idx=\"28\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 50%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   现在把主场交给 Gemini 2.5 Pro，看看它有什么奇妙想法。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img alt=\"image.png\" data-imgfileid=\"503478363\" data-ratio=\"0.45555555555555555\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/eb8669f6-d662-4623-887d-06ce33b3c500/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-original-style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;\" data-index=\"30\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/c30b6592-0c91-4e3a-a61f-ca9a525f7a93/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"29\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   还是非常丝滑～<a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/unlZoM5oCH3HCw2kxy6X_w\"><img src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/0960409e-b0ea-4c59-9460-2978fc6c61b0/1742978739011.png\" style=\"width: 70%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"></a>\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   以上操作 Gemini 2.5 Pro 都是<strong>一次成功，没有报错</strong>。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   最后，我们来检查一下 Gemini 2.5 Pro 的代码审查能力。我们先请 DeepSeek 在代码中植入一些隐藏彩蛋，随后让 Gemini 2.5 Pro 检查修改后的代码。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img alt=\"image.png\" data-imgfileid=\"503478364\" data-ratio=\"0.558974358974359\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6d954c05-0bb7-4d93-cd92-0ad8578eb100/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"975\" data-original-style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;\" data-index=\"31\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/fd45f5f2-158f-4170-a048-3ab04908e171/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"30\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   不出所料，它精准地识别出了问题，给出了标准的专业分析。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img alt=\"image.png\" data-imgfileid=\"503478365\" data-ratio=\"0.34074074074074073\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/91a2a37e-6274-43cc-9e72-11cddd57d600/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-original-style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;\" data-index=\"32\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/660bd566-ec1f-47bb-9ad1-809cf3464d7b/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"31\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   不过，在让众多大模型恼火的鹈鹕骑自行车大赛 svg 绘图大赛中，Gemini 2.5 Pro 还是没打过 Claude 3.7 Sonnet。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img alt=\"图片\" data-imgfileid=\"503478366\" data-ratio=\"0.4638888888888889\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/7ef72da9-7601-4bd7-1f97-2b3ff6784f00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-original-style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);color: rgb(0, 0, 0);letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;\" data-index=\"33\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/522f91a9-eb3c-4781-9888-ee0f59fbd3a6/640.png\" data-report-img-idx=\"32\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <em><sup>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;图左是 Gemini 2.5 pro 生成的，图右是 Claude 3.7 Sonnet 生成的。</sup></em>\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   测到这里，Gemini 2.5 pro 的水平如何，相信读者心中已大概有数了。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   与新版 DeepSeek-V3 不约而同的是，Gemini 2.5 pro 也在编程和逻辑方面加强了不少。最近谷歌在多模态频频发力，不断推动着推理模型原生多模态能力的提升。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   DeepSeek-R1 问世后，我们一直在期待能「强推理、慢思考」的大模型进化成多模态模式。这一突破，是否会由 Gemini 系列率先实现呢？\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <em><sup>参考链接：</sup></em>\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <sup><em>http://aistudio.google.com/app/prompts/new_chat?model=gemini-2.5-pro-exp-03-25</em></sup>\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <sup><em>https://blog.google/technology/google-deepmind/gemini-model-thinking-updates-march-2025</em></sup>\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <em><sup>https://x.com/sundarpichai/status/1904579419496386736</sup></em>\n  </section>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "谷歌 Gemini 2.5 Pro 在推理、编程和多模态能力上表现卓越，多项测试登顶。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "谷歌 Gemini 2.5 Pro 在推理、编程和多模态能力上表现卓越，多项测试登顶。",
  "summary": "文章对谷歌最新发布的 Gemini 2.5 Pro 模型进行了全面评测。该模型在多项基准测试，如 Humanity's Last Exam 等中表现出色，尤其在推理能力方面超越了 OpenAI 的 o3-mini。编程能力也得到显著提升，在 SWE-bench 和 Aider Polyglot 测试中均名列前茅。此外，Gemini 2.5 Pro 在 Chatbot Arena 榜单上以巨大优势登顶，创下了前所未有的分数飞跃，并在复杂指令、编程、数学、创意写作等方面全面领先。该模型延续了 Gemini 系列的原生多模态能力和长上下文窗口优势，支持多种输入模态。通过实际测试，Gemini 2.5 Pro 在推理、数学、科学和编程方面均展现出强大实力，但在某些特定任务上仍有提升空间。",
  "mainPoints": [
